response.overview: After a 4 a.m. knock at the door and haunting voices, Kristen McKay and James Hoyt’s remote getaway becomes a psychological night of terror as three masked strangers invade. Now they must go far beyond what they thought themselves capable of if they hope to survive.
response.tagline: Lock the door. Pretend you're safe.
response.title: The Strangers

results.name: Masked Intruders Attack From Inside the Home
